w.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/author-lb0C1LYxo0fcanV11dmAog">Mạnh Giao</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/X%C3%BA-n%C3%B4-nhi-B%C3%A1c-S%C6%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung-hi%E1%BB%87u-L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%8B-An-th%E1%BB%83/poem-5QwQefTtUPQuXLKUT52-Gg">Xú nô nhi - Bác Sơn đạo trung, hiệu Lý Dị An thể - 醜奴兒－博山道中，效李易安體</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br></div>	</div>
